Folder structure

ML_stock_price_prediction/
│
├── data/
│   ├── raw/             # Original, untouched datasets
│   └── processed/       # Processed, cleaned, or feature-engineered data
│
├── src/
│   ├── data_processing/
|   |   └── data_prep.py
│   ├── visualisation/   # Scripts or modules for creating plots, charts, etc.
│   ├── models/          # Scripts or modules defining model architecture, training loops
│   └── utils/           # Utility functions, helpers, configuration
│
├── requirements.txt     # Python dependencies (pip format)
└── main.py              # Top-level script to orchestrate data processing, model training, evaluation